{"Author": "AnaG", "Date": "on August 17, 2017", "Stars": "5.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "GREAT GIFT", "Text": "I bought it as a christmas gift for my father in law. I was spot on !!! He said it was exactly what he wanted !!! Apparently he uses it and loves it !"}
{"Author": "Scenario", "Date": "on August 15, 2017", "Stars": "1.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Beware: It WILL die and you'll have to start over.", "Text": "Mine died shortly after the 2-year warranty expired. It won't power up. This device has bad capacitors on the power supply, which is a known manufacturing defect. Worse, when yours dies you will have to start over and reprogram everything. In my case, that will take days to get right because I have ~60 devices in my home. The lack of a Load Configuration / Save Configuration from the Cloud feature is pure negligence on INSTEON's part, and I'm surprised there isn't a class-action lawsuit over this."}
